We thank Reviewer 2 for their careful thoughts regarding direct costs in our model. The biological mechanisms behind the forms of direct costs that we modelled were explained in the Introduction of our original manuscript. However we can see that we did not make the link to these mechanisms clear in the Modelling section and that the motivation behind our modelling choices was consequently unclear (see also REVIEWER 1 SPECIFIC COMMENT 4 and our response). 

